scene.message:
Yukino: Yuka looks like she{nl}
doesn't think about anything,{waitkey}{clearbox}but I get the feeling she{nl}
avoids thinking on purpose.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: You guys headed to{nl}
the hospital? The big one out{nl}
on Mikage's northeast edge?{waitkey}{clearbox}That's quite a walk.{nl}
Well, good luck!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Hey, where's Ayase?{nl}
Wasn't she with you guys?{waitkey}{clearbox}We made plans to hang out,{waitkey}{nl}
but she's a total no-show.{nl}
I'm thinking of just{nl}
heading off without her!{waitkey}{clearbox}So weird, she was supposed{nl}
to be looking forward to it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase does this kind of{nl}
thing a lot. Kinda aloof,{waitkey}{clearbox}you never really know what{nl}
she's thinking.{waitkey}{ret}
